{
  "1609370": {
    "name": "Caravanners",
    "steam_appid": 1609370,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Caravanners</strong> 是一款围绕房车和露营展开的轻松探索与生活冒险游戏，设定在一个超大的开放世界中。从一辆小货车开始，购买一辆空的房车，并打造你的梦想露营车。白天探索自然，晚上与朋友围着篝火听音乐、享受生活。🎵🔥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/574a90e992b6a6e04bca501357d69e00.avif?t=1770646605\" width=600 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔓 超大开放世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏕️ 多样的区域和生态环境</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌄 动态天气系统：雨、雾、晴、雪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👥 单人或1-4人合作游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 执行不同任务赚取金钱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚙️ 精细的内外部自定义系统，打造你的风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌔 日夜循环，不同时间有不同氛围</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏕️ 房车就是你的家，世界就是你的营地</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚌 与朋友组建多个房车车队同行</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 一个无尽而不会无聊的冒险等待着你</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索广阔的开放世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个可供你自由探索的大型世界：湖泊、海洋、森林、岛屿、村庄、山脉、秘密地点、小镇以及各种独特区域！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/b92c9827b0699b3b648f979eddc8faf2.avif?t=1770646605\" width=1000 height=784 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/68df98e6b65c16bb455dcc28036968c0.poster.avif?t=1770646605\" width=700 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/68df98e6b65c16bb455dcc28036968c0.webm?t=1770646605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/68df98e6b65c16bb455dcc28036968c0.mp4?t=1770646605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的房车，就是你的家</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍲 在冰箱里储存食物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍳 做饭解决饥饿问题</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛋️ 坐在沙发上欣赏风景、听音乐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪟 开关窗帘，打造属于你的氛围</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡 控制车内灯光开关</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚽 使用你的车载厕所</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛺️ 打开帐篷，布置你独特的营地</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/778ae2498a1e611e1f0d15110215239a.poster.avif?t=1770646605\" width=700 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/778ae2498a1e611e1f0d15110215239a.webm?t=1770646605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/778ae2498a1e611e1f0d15110215239a.mp4?t=1770646605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造属于你的梦想营地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个人或与朋友一起从零开始建造属于你的营地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用模块化系统自由组合搭建营地</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌄 无论是湖边、森林深处，每个地方都可以扎营</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪑 摆放桌椅</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 生一堆篝火</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎶 播放你喜欢的音乐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥩 烧烤食物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧘 与朋友一起放松、享受生活</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/069f71fcc08144652a332b2d7a08d022.poster.avif?t=1770646605\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/069f71fcc08144652a332b2d7a08d022.webm?t=1770646605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/069f71fcc08144652a332b2d7a08d022.mp4?t=1770646605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >资源管理系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理饥饿、口渴、睡眠、如厕、燃油、食物、金钱和声誉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >外观与内饰自定义</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/b42e0e2c49a52ca14fbd27accb383c6a.avif?t=1770646605\" width=600 height=194 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/b8c7ac95c357e0ba4821cf25f2b8ca6c.poster.avif?t=1770646605\" width=700 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/b8c7ac95c357e0ba4821cf25f2b8ca6c.webm?t=1770646605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/b8c7ac95c357e0ba4821cf25f2b8ca6c.mp4?t=1770646605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >车辆外部定制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >车身、轮胎、保险杠颜色可自定义</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可替换轮毂和保险杠风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >贴纸与皮肤系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >添加各种配件</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造独一无二的外观风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/bb67d2d8500e57275a066d11c94f3459.poster.avif?t=1770646605\" width=700 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/bb67d2d8500e57275a066d11c94f3459.webm?t=1770646605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609370/extras/bb67d2d8500e57275a066d11c94f3459.mp4?t=1770646605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>家具布置系统</strong> – <strong>打造你梦想的生活空间</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择不同风格的墙面、地板和天花板材质</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择沙发、橱柜、窗帘与装饰品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >添加冰箱、烧烤架、水槽、马桶等设备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✅<strong>别忘了将游戏加入愿望单！✅</strong></h2>",
